# ── Face recognition photos (private) ─────────────
# The images/ folder ships with placeholder structure only.
# Add your own photos locally — never commit real faces to a public repo.
images/*.jpeg
images/*.jpg
images/*.png
images/*.webp

# ── ML model artifacts ─────────────────────────────
# Large binary files — tracked via Git LFS or excluded entirely
# Uncomment the line below if you are NOT using Git LFS:
# AQI-MONITOR/ml/*.pt
# AQI-MONITOR/ml/*.npy
# AQI-MONITOR/ml/*.pkl

